results.title: ASKANI'SON (1996) #4
results.description: Nathan takes on the title of Askani’son, after Madame Sanctity announces him to her followers. During the reveling, Aliya pulls Nathan aside and encourages him to re-think his allegiance to Sanctity. She reveals that her teacher has been going mad for some time, and that Sanctity encourages a hive-mind mentality. Nathan now believes that it is Aliya, and not Madame Sanctity, who is destined to become his teacher.

results.title: Classic Star Wars: Devilworlds (1996) #2
results.description: There are more than fifty billion droids at work throughout the galaxy, doing the jobs better handled by hard metal than by soft flesh. Human muscles strain and grow weak, and Human hearts grow weary of toil and indignity; droids have no such problems. They have no bones, and they have no souls. And when Humans grow old and feeble, they must be cared for, must be clothed and fed, that is their right. But droids have no rights, and so they end up here, in the vast, corroded canyons of Ronyards.
